{"tid":2175673,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB免費電視蝕逾5億 廣告收入跌七成","createTime":"2020-08-26T15:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T06:22:26.000Z","uid":339805,"like":485,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0ddb14afc610bda70bd3372958957df164379c","tid":2175673,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"電視廣播（0511）（TVB）公布6月底止中期業績，期內收入按年大減38%至只有12.26億元，並且由盈轉虧，股東應佔虧損達2.93億元，並且首度不派中期息。該集團表示，會於年底參考全年業績及業務前景後，審視是否派付任何末期股息。<br />\n<br />\nTVB指出，集團的免費電視廣告收入只有3.51億元，按年大減69%，不過由於更多家庭觀眾留在家中抗疫，黃金時段劇集收視率顯著上升，惟無法扭轉虧損命運，整體由盈轉虧，虧損高達5.15億元。其OTT業務myTV SUPER的訂戶收入雖然按年增長16%至1.46億元，但是廣收入則按年減少46%至5300萬元，因此該部門整體收入按年跌11%至2.02億元，獲利只100萬元，按年大減96%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1598448763833&amp;issue=20200826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1598448763833%26issue%3D20200826&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=9d715c5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1598448763833&amp;issue=20200826</a>"},{"pid":"08fde5d483547bfa17c69e30605c5c4adccb4e01","tid":2175673,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc7a1ce19954b28e3d1cd91c746891c1bc743c1","tid":2175673,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fb78418a5cdfd03736bbc602d73991cf9f860f","tid":2175673,"uid":287751,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>借個位 請幫推<br />\n831 有行動</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">【行動 Post 請置頂】八三一週年，手足歸隊啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2175581\" data-auto-link target=\"_b